name: Cookie Dunk Dunk
blurb: Cookie Dunk Dunk is a strategy based skill/puzzle game with amazing graphics, minigames, and cookies with personalities.

rewards.reward: No Reward

Thank You Pack---------------------------\r\n- We will send you a digital version of one of our awesome wallpapers that you can use to decorate any of your devices (resolutions are for iPhone, iPad, and Computer).\r\n- We will personally mail you a thank you letter with a crayon drawing of one of our cookie characters.

Wallpaper Pack----------------------------\r\n- We will send you a digital set of all 5 of our awesome wallpapers that you can use to decorate any of your devices (resolutions are for iPhone, iPad, and Computer).\r\n- We will personally mail you a thank you letter with a crayon drawing of one of our cookie characters.
Supporter Pack----------------------------\r\n- Your name in the Special Thanks section of the credits.\r\n- Also includes: Wallpaper Pack

Digital Pack---------------------------------
- A PDF file of our beautiful concept art book.
- A digital copy of our catchy soundtrack (in mp3 format).
- A digital copy of our hilarious vocal bloopers.
- Your name in the Special Thanks section of the credits.
- Also includes: Supporter Pack
Pad Pack------------------------------------\r\n- A Cookie Dunk Dunk themed mousepad.\r\n- Also includes: Digital Pack
Hat Pack------------------------------------\r\n- A baseball cap embroidered with the Cookie Dunk Dunk Logo.\r\n- Also includes: Digital Pack
Shirt Pack-----------------------------------\r\n- A t-shirt printed with either one of our cookies or the Cookie Dunk Dunk Logo, chosen at random.\r\n- Also includes: Digital Pack
Mug Pack-----------------------------------\r\n- A coffee mug printed with either one of our cookies or the Cookie Dunk Dunk Logo, chosen at random.\r\n- Also includes: Digital Pack

Paraphernalia Pack-----------------------
- A baseball cap embroidered with the Cookie Dunk Dunk Logo.
- A t-shirt printed with either one of our cookies or the Cookie Dunk Dunk Logo, chosen at random.
- A Cookie Dunk Dunk themed mousepad.
- A coffee mug printed with either one of our cookies or the Cookie Dunk Dunk Logo, chosen at random.
- Also includes: Digital Pack

Old School Pack---------------------------
- A physical, hardcover copy of our beautiful concept art book and autographed by our team.
- A physical, CD copy of our catchy soundtrack and autographed by our team.
- Also includes: Digital Pack
Modern Pack-------------------------------\r\n- A custom 8GB USB drive, with all digital content in this pack stored inside.\r\n- Also includes: Old School Pack

Small Poster Pack-------------------------
- A set of collectible cards with characters from the game.
- A 11"x17" poster of one of the Cookie Dunk Dunk planets.
- Also includes: Modern Pack

Large Poster Pack-------------------------
- A set of collectible cards with characters from the game.
- A 24"x36" poster of one of the Cookie Dunk Dunk planets.
- Also includes: Modern Pack

Snuggle Pack------------------------------
- A Cookie Dunk Dunk themed pillow case (pillow not included.)
- A plushie of one of our adorable cookies or milk monster (customer's choice).
- Also includes: Digital Pack
Cookie Pack--------------------------------\r\n- A 3 inch, 3D printed model of one of our cookies (customer's choice).\r\n- Also includes: Snuggle Pack
Super Cookie Pack------------------------\r\n- A 4 inch, 3D printed model of one of our super cookies (customer's choice).\r\n- Also includes: Snuggle Pack
Interview Pack-----------------------------\r\n- A 30 minute Skype chat with our CEO and lead programmer (sound and art leads available upon request).\r\n- Also includes: Digital Pack
Milk Monster Pack------------------------\r\n- A 7 inch, 3D printed model of the Milk Monster.\r\n- Also includes: Snuggle Pack
Planet Pack---------------------------------\r\n- A softball sized, 3D printed model of one of the planets in the Cookie Dunk Dunk universe (customer's choice).\r\n- Also includes: Snuggle Pack

Collector's Pack---------------------------
- A 3 inch, 3D printed model of one of our cookies (customer's choice).
- A 4 inch, 3D printed model of one of our super cookies (customer's choice).
- A 7 inch, 3D printed model of the Milk Monster.
- A softball sized, 3D printed model of one of the planets in the Cookie Dunk Dunk universe (customer's choice).
- Also includes: Paraphernalia Pack
- Also includes: Large Poster Pack
- Also includes: Snuggle Pack
iPod Pack-----------------------------------\r\n- A custom iPod engraved with one of our cookies or game logo (customer's choice).\r\n- Also includes: Digital Pack

Cookie Designer Pack--------------------
- Help design a custom cookie (Oatmeal, Pokke, etc.)
- A 3 inch, 3D model of your cookie design.
- Also includes: Digital Pack
iPhone Pack--------------------------------\r\n- A custom iPhone engraved with one of our cookies or game logo (customer's choice).\r\n- Also includes: Digital Pack
iPad Pack-----------------------------------\r\n- A custom iPad engraved with one of our cookies or game logo (customer's choice).\r\n- Also includes: Digital Pack

7 Gun Pack---------------------------------
- A 46"x28" flag emblazoned with our 7Gun logo.
- An acoustic guitar with the 7 Gun logo, hand painted by Duane (CEO).
- Also includes: Collector's Pack

Single Cookie Costume Designer Pack------------------------------------------
- Work with our artists to create one of the costumes for one of our cookies for a cookie costume pack.
- A 4 inch, 3D printed model of your cookie design.
- Also includes: Digital Pack

Cookie Costume Designer Pack--------
- Work with our artists to create the 7 costumes for our cookies for a cookie costume pack.
- A 4 inch, 3D printed model of one of your cookies (customer's choice).
- Also includes: Digital Pack

World Designer Pack----------------------
- Work with our artists to create a planet for the Cookie Dunk Dunk universe.
- Work with our artists and programmers to create a concept for your planet's mini-game.
- Work with our artists to create the 7 costumes for our cookies for a cookie costume pack.
- A softball sized, 3D printed model of your planet design
- Also includes: Digital Pack

Wearable Cookie Costume Pack-------
- A cookie costume based off of one of our cookie characters
- A baseball cap embroidered with the Cookie Dunk Dunk Logo.
- A t-shirt printed with either one of our cookies or the Cookie Dunk Dunk Logo, chosen at random.
- A coffee mug printed with either one of our cookies or the Cookie Dunk Dunk Logo, chosen at random.
- A jacket with the Cookie Dunk Dunk logo
- A patch with the Cookie Dunk Dunk logo 
- We will personally mail you a thank you letter with a crayon drawing of one of our cookie characters.
- Also includes: Digital Pack

Vacationer's Pack-------------------------
- We will fly you down to spend the day with our team.
- Go for a night on the town with the team when work is over.
- Have the opportunity to record your voice for use in the game.
- Also includes: Snuggle Pack
- Also includes: Large Poster Pack
- Also includes: Paraphenalia Pack

Adopt a CEO for a Day Pack------------
- Our CEO, Duane Schor, will personally fly out to your city for the day and give a speech at any event you are hosting.
- A wallet with the Cookie Dunk Dunk logo embroidered into it (includes an autographed photo of Duane).
- Duane will work with you to create a custom art piece for you.
- Also includes: Paraphernalia Pack
- Also includes: Large Poster Pack
